Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:35.64,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HDC9D69&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}啊啊 女神的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩笑开大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？小蓓儿也想尝尝我做的菜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊？干嘛莫名其妙闯进别人家做饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 饭还没做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子都快饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了 亲爱的 乖乖等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊 快点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 萤一 等等 萤一！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 于是就变成这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是看错你了 萤一 已经有姐姐了还和菲尔德这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍无可忍了！萤一 你到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还问我？明明已经有姐姐了…虽然姐姐是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 诗寇蒂也来尝尝吧 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要吃菲尔德做的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 要是比小蓓儿做的还好吃就麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来试试啊 看看到底可不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？对小孩子来说太过刺激了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受操纵的迹象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 饭粒粘在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦 蓓儿丹蒂她们在看着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 她们都很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我不知道你有什么企图 但要是这孩子生气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是升龙之柱 哇 南无阿弥陀佛南无阿弥陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓…蓓儿丹蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不够成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 挖出好大一块
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都没挖过耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反应 没有使用魔力的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那萤一被魔族附体的可能性呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不可能 萤一是真货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德也没头绪吗？会不会萤一吃了爱的种子之类的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经调查过了 没有吃过药的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那萤一真的对菲尔德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 绝对有古怪…绝对有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 一起洗澡吧 很久没一起洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想跟我一起洗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…我会害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛要含羞 我和你是彼此相爱的 没关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 要是让蓓儿丹蒂看到他们一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近一带就要化为灰烬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先做好防范措施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去这里都会消失 这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又自说自话决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？我现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 我们互相搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌！萤一大色鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看这里 快出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好道歉的吧 她只是个孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 诗寇蒂 那种话要等变成大人了才能说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 睡在那里会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底对萤一做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在恋爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到此为止 STOP！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的企图老老实实说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是蓓儿丹蒂找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想象的快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事？你想要萤一的心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 可能只是心血来潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心血来潮？就因为那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的话就来抢回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂 去吧 夺回萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好像一点都不着急 真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在看好戏啦 真是让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神真不错 让人好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之名兀儿德 以掌管过去之时之女神之名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们送往时之缝隙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一原来住在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然不该乱动引擎的 这样是赢不了那个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一好可爱 萤一！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 现在的萤一还没和我们相遇呢 不可能认识你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎又熄火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萤 先走一步咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是桂马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总有一天你要超越他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 我好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 打情骂俏的 真是看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 这时候的萤一很没女人缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到已经和萤一认识了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经计算到我们的行动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我们往过去到哪里 她都比我们更早一步认识萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大魔界长要做到这个很容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能让他回心转意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安静一下 虽然有点突然…给大家介绍一位转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫蓓儿丹蒂 日语很好 应该很快就能融入大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蓓儿丹蒂 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿…丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看吧 小蓓儿你真正的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我是小学生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是大人了 应该进姐姐的班级吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经作为小学生办了转学手续了 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 诗寇蒂小朋友 教室在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（请看左边的三角形  顶点ABC……）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就要从情书开始 听好 给他的时候一定要故作姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天就到这里 考试会考的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 我并不是有意看你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得好漂亮…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 数学笔记能借我看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了 不愧是萤一 写得真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有你说的那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 你头发又睡乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看书了 一起打篮球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 如果可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 你在干什么啊 快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么拿不出这点勇气 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没交给他？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能输给那家伙的妨碍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要让对方注意自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗送秋波 故意跌倒让他看到裙底春光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者问他喜欢的女生类型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里总有挥之不去的阴影…就像充满了邪恶的念头…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确不适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 改变作战计划 那家伙就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要好好向萤一传达心意就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样总能做到了吧？不 你必须做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂 去儿童商店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿童商店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是糖果店 玩具和糖果点心有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以请客你一些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学生也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕去哪里玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 今天没带钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借一步说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哼哼 来这一招了啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我不知道菲尔德做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会听你说的 能不能把那个先放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多管闲事 你先走吧 我很快就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好无聊得紧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料你也撑不过5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小看我的话会吃苦头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹车失灵了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我萤一？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你第一次就直接叫名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…对萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在这种地方和别的女人聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机车倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 你没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 蓓儿丹蒂 大魔界长太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 她在看着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 你真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的…心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你很恨我吧 最爱的人被夺走 像现在这样手挽手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随意地任我玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这种事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖别动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样 这就是你真正的心意…以及力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把现在的感情释放出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨 愤怒 嫉妒 把你心中的那些向我发泄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样萤一就能恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就能独占他了哦 来 让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的一切都解放出来吧 伴随着你的力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢雪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白雪白的 仿佛能够净化人的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得和你很相称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 钻石星辰！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 我有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概做了不好的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…你其实并不喜欢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会被区区人类看穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是萤一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要为了蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让电话连通到天界 能向魔物挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么地方都能毫不犹豫地前往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊 人家还想看小蓓儿真正的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 这不明摆着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真正的心意就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…蓓儿丹蒂…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我一起去博物馆参观吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 不过要5年以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我在这里干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年后…有什么事来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和萤一一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来会是什么颜色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我记得应该是…橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂 你喜欢雪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次一起去看雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抛下的古老约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会忘记 总有一天要完成约定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 啊啊 各自的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在等着呢
